overview: Ultimate Death Match is back, and Shane Douglas wants to settle some scores. As the FBI closes in on the crooked Jake Reed, bodies pile up and a sinister player makes a move on the UDM franchise. Featuring Larry Zbyszko, Tommy Dreamer, Ted DiBiase, Ricky Morton, Loki, Val Venus, Raven, Dr. Steve and Johnny Swinger.
title: Ultimate Death Match 3
